### Congressional Data Resources

I maintain a comprehensive guide to working with congressional data in R:

**Congressional Data Guide**: [congressdata.joshuamccrain.com](http://congressdata.joshuamccrain.com/)

This resource provides tutorials and guides on:
- Working with congressional datasets
- Data manipulation and analysis in R
- Regression discontinuity methods
- Statistical modeling with political data

